      <title>巴里克可能因与政府的争端而关闭马里金矿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/barrick-may-close-mali-gold-mine-over-dispute-with-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴里克黄金公司表示，马里军政府已经阻止了该国最大金矿的货运，如果货运继续暂停，该公司将需要停止该矿的作业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/barrick-may-close-mali-gold-mine-over-dispute-with-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 12:56:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
